<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.9">
<l>maṇṇum malaiyum maṟikaṭalka ḷummaṟṟum yāvumellām</l>
<l>tiṇṇam viḻuṅkiyumiḻn tatēvaṉaic cikkeṉa nāṭutirē</l>
<l>leṇṇaṟ kariyatōrē ṉamāki yirunilam pukkiṭantu</l>
<l>vaṇṇak karuṅkuḻal mātarōṭu maṇantāṉaik kaṇṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you are consistently seeking the deity</l>
<l rend="indent">who swallowed whole the earth, the mountains,</l>
<l>the crashing seas and all else, [and then] spit [them] out,</l>
<l>there are those who saw the one,</l>
<l rend="indent">as an inconceivably rare boar</l>
<l rend="indent">pierced and dug out the vast earth,</l>
<l>who married the beautiful, dark haired lady.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
